== Overview ==
Bulk Shield The Baron (mushroom) class shield generator provides a basic energy barrier offering protection against light weapons fire.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Baron Shield can be bought in the workshop, or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.
